title: Converse Rubber Tracks: I Am Lightyear "Lose Myself" Music Video
description:
Check out the original music video created by Habib Yazdi for I Am Lightyear, who recorded her song "Lose Myself" at the Converse Rubber Tracks studio. 

Converse's A/V Connection project pairs artists and filmmakers together to collaborate on music videos for tracks recorded at the Converse Rubber Tracks Studio.
Director: Habib Yazdi
Directors of Photography: Andrew Synowiez + Frank Sun
Producer: King Lu
Choreographer: Leah Wilks
Make-up: Kristina Zmaic
Assistant Director: Samir Rao
Gaffer: Steve Milligan
Key Grip: Matt Lawless
Assistant Camera: Yi Zhu
Key Production Assistant: Shelby Aileen Nash
Production Assistants: Christina Huang, Yinuo Vera, Mandy Jiang, Amber
Oliver
Drummers: Austin McCall, Will Ridenour, Robert Cantrell, Rocky Iwashima
Special Thanks to: Converse, Cornerstone, Balloons & Tunes, Sarah Riazati,
Karli Stein, Lauren Glucksman, Joseph Marra, Amy Zhang, Marie Garlock,
Kaitlin Houlditch-Fair, Kristen Winter
